==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nummulation
<hw>Num`mu*la"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Physiol.)</fld> <def>The arrangement of the red blood corpuscles
in rouleaux, like piles of coins, as when a drop of human blood is
examined under the microscope.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nummulite</ent>⟦br⟧
